description: React functional component 'EmptyState' that displays a message when there's no activity data in the dashboard. It includes functionality for admins to seed sample data in development mode by making an API call.

methods.name: EmptyState({ onDataSeeded })
methods.description: React component that renders a UI for empty dashboard state with options to seed sample data for admins in development mode.

methods.name: handleSeed
methods.description: Asynchronous event handler that triggers seeding of sample data through an API call, updates component state, and handles errors.
